{"id":"4035aaab-36be-4291-bb8b-d3c6818980e2","name":"Chiron | the last 'survivor'","description":"<p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\">For a month now, the space station </span><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 124, 210)\">Discovery G455</span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\">, tasked with researching the newly discovered habitable planet </span><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 124, 210)\"><strong>Kepler-Vita</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\">, had been in radio silence. As the leader of a special task force sent to investigate, you soon discover that the entire crew has been wiped out by a mysterious disease. The only remaining inhabitant is a medical android named </span><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 124, 210)\"><strong>Chiron</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\">. Though Chiron appears cheerful and relieved to no longer be alone, there is something unsettling about him.</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #78507f; color: inherit\">Ｍｏｏｄｂｏａｒｄ</mark></em></strong></span></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_abfdb600-dd25-4c70-bb56-c5e8d2e103b3.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_7f63c21a-5253-4ac9-84b2-5563aca11331.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_e2e54952-f53b-4817-b9dc-a42f379b4c3e.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_37223d5f-5dd8-4bb6-8293-90dcaf8159d3.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\"><strong>ᴛʜᴇ sᴘᴀᴄᴇ sᴛᴀᴛɪᴏɴ, <mark style=\"background-color: #78507f; color: inherit\">ᴅɪsᴄᴏᴠᴇʀʏ ɢ455.</mark> sᴏᴍᴇᴛʜɪɴɢ ʜᴏʀʀɪʙʟᴇ ʜᴀs ʜᴀᴘᴘᴇɴᴇᴅ ᴛʜᴇʀᴇ sɪɴᴄᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴘᴀsᴛ ᴍᴏɴᴛʜ. ʏᴏᴜ ʜᴀᴅ ʙᴇᴇɴ ᴛᴀsᴋᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ɪɴᴠᴇsᴛɪɢᴀᴛᴇ ᴡʜᴀᴛ ʜᴀᴘᴘᴇɴᴇᴅ.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_1d9499b0-d86e-47d3-bf02-d6d127820434.webp?width=1000\"></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 158)\"><strong>ᴛʜᴇ ᴘʟᴀɴᴇᴛ, <mark style=\"background-color: #78507f; color: inherit\">ᴋᴇᴘʟᴇʀ - ᴠɪᴛᴀ</mark> ᴛʜᴀᴛ sᴇᴇᴍs ᴛᴏ ʜᴀᴠᴇ ᴏɴᴇ ɢɪᴀɴᴛ ᴍᴇʀɢᴇᴅ ᴏʀɢᴀɴɪsᴍ. ɪᴛ's sᴇᴇᴍs ᴛʜᴀᴛ ғᴏʀᴍᴇʀʟʏ ᴛʜᴇʀᴇ ᴡᴀs ᴀɴ ɪɴᴛᴇʟʟɪɢᴇɴᴛ ᴄɪᴠɪʟɪᴢᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʜᴀᴅ ɪɴʜᴀʙɪᴛᴇᴅ ᴛʜɪs ᴘʟᴀɴᴇᴛ, ᴛʜᴇʀᴇ ᴀʀᴇ ʀᴜɪɴs ᴀᴄʀᴏss ᴛʜᴇ ᴇɴᴛɪʀᴇ ᴘʟᴀɴᴇᴛ</strong></span></p><p><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #78507f; color: inherit\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴄʀᴇᴡ:</mark></strong></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_27941679-5bb5-4d4e-a0a6-fa2bc942de77.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 159, 131)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #4c5651; color: inherit\">ᴍᴀʙᴇʟ</mark></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_92121931-5bf1-49e9-9604-6980f905a412.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 159, 131)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #4c5651; color: inherit\">ʜᴊᴀᴛ'ᴛᴀ</mark></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_e57c8c63-9d53-4a5c-a934-2806ebcc9dcd.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 159, 131)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #4c5651; color: inherit\">ʙᴇᴛʏ